N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 331.2 - Applications forwarded to division

State Regulations

An application received in the first instance by any agency
or any board of elections of the State of New York shall be forwarded promptly
to the division for record purposes. Notes
